00:02:09.000 --> 00:02:12.000
A spin off of the beloved saga of Shrek,

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:15.000
Puss in Boots is starring the legendary booted cat and

00:02:15.000 --> 00:02:19.000
tells his adventures before he met the green ogre,

00:02:19.000 --> 00:02:23.000
when he was friends with Humpty Dumpty and Kitty, the cat of the road.

00:02:23.000 --> 00:02:25.000
In the original version,

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:28.000
the protagonists are voiced by Antonio Banderas,

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:30.000
Zach Galifianakis and Salma Hayek.

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:32.000
The movie will be released in December 2011.

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:36.000
Kristen Stewart will play Snow White!

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:38.000
The producer Palak Patel has in fact confirmed

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:43.000
on twitter that Kristen will star the film re-adaptation

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:45.000
of the famous fairy tale by the Brothers Grimm,

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:47.000
Snow White and the Seven Dwarfs.

00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:49.000
Filming starts this summer in London,

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:52.000
Scotland and Germany and in the cast will also appear

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:54.000
Viggo Mortensen and Charlize Theron.

00:02:54.000 --> 00:02:55.000
It's all for today,

